♫  I love you  ♫

137
00:09:42,140 --> 00:09:48,590
♫  I always have  ♫

138
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:52,390
- Doctor.
- Yes.

139
00:09:52,390 --> 00:09:55,040
The loser buys ice cream.

140
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:56,080
Sounds good.

141
00:09:56,080 --> 00:10:03,570
♫  I am the most grateful for that  ♫

142
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:13,070
♫  Do you remember what I've told you before?  ♫

143
00:10:13,070 --> 00:10:18,640
♫  When I think of you, it gets better.  ♫

144
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:19,700
♫  In the unknown days,   ♫

145
00:10:19,700 --> 00:10:22,390
This one.

